description: This skill reads the latest headlines from Good Housekeeping. Categories include home ideas, health, life, beauty, food and recipesâ€‹ , and holidays. Users can start the skill by saying "Alexa, open good house keeping" and then ask for the available categories. They can choose which category they wish to hear the headlines from and change the category at any time. When Alexa asks if they want to continue, users can say keep going to continue or no, stop , cancel to end the skill.
exampleInteractions: I would like to hear home ideas.
name: Good House Keeping
shortDescription: Good Housekeeping is your destination for everything from recipes to product reviews to home decor inspiration.
